{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Change the law for pet food so manufacturers have to announce recipe change",
        "additional_details": "My dog has a severe chicken allergy and sensitive foods which start off with no chicken in, secretly add chicken or chicken oil which causes him severe pain, sickness and diarrhoea. Many dogs have this same allergy as well as many others.",
        "background": "I want parliament to enforce pet food companies to have to announce when they add or change recipes by adding a sticker to all bags containing this new recipe. \r\nMany animals have allergies and companies change recipes without any warning making pet owners have to figure out why their pets are ill.",
